INTEROP: what is the TV remote of the metaverse? How do we toggle between specialized virtual worlds both web2 and Web3 seamlessly? I want to hang w my yoga friends in the morning in one virtual world, but want to play esports in the afternoon somewhere else. ğŸ“º
SOCIAL INFRA: clarity and paved paths on reg, tax, accounting treatment, navigation of local jurisdictional rules, and community based governance set up âš–ï¸
FUTURE WORKFORCE: more 3d designers and architects, community and DAO managers, metaverse experience experts who specialize in tokenomics and engagement, more storytellers ğŸ’ªğŸ¼

TECH: performance across devices (inc mobile) w definition of metadata standards for wearables, objects, to enable unique manifestations of NFTs in different virtual worlds. Eg an NFT is a t-shirt in Decentraland but a sword in a fantasy game (h/t @coin_artist for pioneering) ğŸ‘©ğŸ»â€ğŸ’»

PRIVACY & ID: in addition to using verifiable credentials to support multiple anon avatars for compliant payments and cyber bullying prevention, expansion of NFT token gated spaces to create more opportunities for private interactions and business meetings. ğŸ¤«

DEFI + DAOs: Evolution of NFT asset backed financing (virtual world mortgages) leveraging DeFi primatives; alongside an emergence of cross border and cross metaverse FX and liquidity & token treasury mgmt solutions; w/ DAO tooling for community, neighborhood, and tribe management

COMMERCIAL INFRA: A delightful wallet experience that combines tradfi payments rails, crypto & NFTs, digital identity verifiable credentials, with the ability to support a variety of anon avatars across virtual worlds while still making private KYC/AML compliant payments ğŸ’¸
